    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/a4a58ae0023bc776db1ac4efd62b4b95.poster.avif?t=1763750024\" aria-label=\" EMBARK ON A MUSICAL ADVENTURE Will you unite the splintered pantheon of Norwyn to defeat Mar, the Queen of Terror? Fight, jump, and dodge obstacles and menacing enemies as you ski further into the darkness that has befallen the snow-covered land of Norwyn.\" width=616 height=646 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/a4a58ae0023bc776db1ac4efd62b4b95.webm?t=1763750024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/a4a58ae0023bc776db1ac4efd62b4b95.mp4?t=1763750024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/4b44b4d18df4aa415a64e010eafe1f26.avif?t=1763750024\" alt=\"&amp;quot;My latest rhythm game obsession!&amp;quot; – VICE  &amp;quot;The best game we saw at PAX East.&amp;quot; – But Why Tho  &amp;quot;The best parts of Hades and Sayonara Wild Hearts.&amp;quot; – Digital Trends  &amp;quot;Fresh Tracks was a breakout hit on the PAX Expo floor, and for good reason.&amp;quot; – CBR\" width=616 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/12b271d17c8ac58fbab074e82344873e.poster.avif?t=1763750024\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/12b271d17c8ac58fbab074e82344873e.webm?t=1763750024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/c195d21c623d4e5e2b75b9d4dece736f.poster.avif?t=1763750024\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/c195d21c623d4e5e2b75b9d4dece736f.webm?t=1763750024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/8fcbbc7e67a1ccdcd4d8de8bc7aba185.avif?t=1763750024\" alt=\"MEET THE MYTHICS SOGVAR, THE GOD OF METAL Voiced by Peter Stormare (Fargo, American Gods, Constantine, Until Dawn) The Mythic of Adventure. A fiery narrator of chaos and glory who lives for epic battles, legendary heroes, and crushing guitar riffs. Sogvar tells your tale like it’s the last song before the world ends.  FARS &amp;amp; DRAM, THE GODS OF ORCHESTRA Dram voiced by Michael Antonakos (Assassin’s Creed Odyssey, Gotham Knights) Fars voiced by Ian Hanlin (Sonic Prime, LEGO Jurassic World) Joy and sorrow. Comedy and tragedy. Two minds, one god. Their music swings between laughter and heartbreak, binding Skaii’s story in theatrical extremes.  KODA, THE GODDESS OF POP Voiced by Ceara Morgana (Starship Troopers: Extermination, Super Team Canada) Hope incarnate. Koda was the first to share Story-Songs with humanity. Her voice heals, uplifts, and keeps the Mythics from tearing themselves apart—most of the time.  MAR, THE QUEEN OF TERROR Voiced by Bethany Brown (The 100, Chilling Adventures of Sabrina) Mar’s nightmare-fueled rhymes cut deep—and hide painful truths.\" width=616 height=1078 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202950/extras/39f2fbaae6a8d67ea5f1184eeb9bc913.avif?t=1763750024\" alt=\"Features\" width=616 height=115 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rhythm-Driven Gameplay</strong>: Movement, combat, and progression seamlessly sync with a dynamic, evolving soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story-Rich with Full Voice Acting: </strong>Meet the Mythics, the Gods of Norwyn, through story and song - all fully voiced by legends like Peter Stormare (Fargo, Until Dawn) and Michael Antonakos (Assassin's Creed Odyssey, Gotham Knights).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High Replayability</strong>: Roguelite mechanics encourage skiers to refine their skills while unlocking upgrades and strategies for future runs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Deeply Immersive Soundtrack</strong>: Get in the flow with Fresh Tracks’ rich, genre-crossing 28-track soundtrack that surprises with each new beat track and dynamically responds to your every movement.</p></li></ul>",
